<title>Syncfusion - Smart Scheduler Samples</title>

<h4 style="text-align:center;">Smart Scheduler</h4>

@inject IJSRuntime JSRuntime

<div class="scheduler-ai-container">
    <Description>
        <p>The <b>Smart Scheduler</b> integrates with the Syncfusion Smart Paste Button Component, enabling users to transform selected content directly into scheduler events. In the Smart Scheduler, the Smart Paste Component intelligently analyzes the data and automatically creates corresponding events in the scheduler, streamlining the scheduling process and saving time.</p>
